commands.name: az webapp log deployment list
commands.summary: List deployments associated with web app.
examples: az webapp log deployment list --name MyWebApp --resource-group MyResourceGroup

commands.name: az webapp log deployment show
commands.summary: Show deployment logs of the latest deployment, or a specific deployment if deployment-id is specified.
examples: az webapp log deployment show --name MyWebApp --resource-group MyResourceGroup
az webapp log deployment show --name MyWebApp --resource-group MyResourceGroup --deployment-id MyDeploymentId
